*WHAT*
*:robot_face:<https://githubnext.com/copilot-for-prs-sunset|[deprecated]> Generated by Copilot at <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/commit/bf5fef54fa1e76503309d1e045cd55b0090c8ac0|bf5fef5>*

Refactor daily rounds form component to clone previous log values more easily.

*Proposed Changes*

• Fixes <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/issues/6602|#6602>?
• Made fields visible regardless of whether "copy values from previous log?" is checked or not.
• Keeping the checkbox unchecked by default as requested in issue.
• When checkbox is clicked values from previous log get copied to form field. when it's unchecked that resets the form to initial state.

@ohcnetwork/care-fe-code-reviewers @ohcnetwork/code-reviewers

*Merge Checklist*

☐ Add specs that demonstrate bug / test a new feature.
☐ Update <https://docs.coronasafe.network/coronasafe-care-documentation/architecture/architecture-and-layering-of-care|product documentation>.
☐ Ensure that UI text is kept in I18n files.
☑︎ Prep screenshot or demo video for changelog entry, and attach it to issue.
☑︎ Request for Peer Reviews
☐ Completion of QA

*HOW*
*:robot_face:<https://githubnext.com/copilot-for-prs-sunset|[deprecated]> Generated by Copilot at <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/commit/bf5fef54fa1e76503309d1e045cd55b0090c8ac0|bf5fef5>*

• Simplify the initial state of the form and errors by using the initForm and initError constants directly (<https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/pull/6659/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-2b725d1dcc3aabbc0438aff687d8c29b79847cde3ea5e171e86ca113a4e6a612L70-R71|link>)
• Replace the hasPreviousLog state variable with a previousLog state variable that stores the data of the previous log, if any (<https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/pull/6659/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-2b725d1dcc3aabbc0438aff687d8c29b79847cde3ea5e171e86ca113a4e6a612L110-R111|link>, <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/pull/6659/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-2b725d1dcc3aabbc0438aff687d8c29b79847cde3ea5e171e86ca113a4e6a612L180-R181|link>)
• Set the clone_last form field to false by default, instead of using the count of the previous logs as a condition (<https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/pull/6659/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-2b725d1dcc3aabbc0438aff687d8c29b79847cde3ea5e171e86ca113a4e6a612L195-R196|link>)
• Add a new function clonePreviousLog that copies the values from the previousLog state variable to the form state variable, except for some fields that should not be cloned (<https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/pull/6659/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-2b725d1dcc3aabbc0438aff687d8c29b79847cde3ea5e171e86ca113a4e6a612R393-R413|link>)
• Modify the rendering logic of the form fields based on the clone_last form field value (<https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/pull/6659/files?diff=unified&w=0#diff-2b725d1dcc3aabbc0438aff687d8c29b79847cde3ea5e171e86ca113a4e6a612L453-R656|link>)
